prodNameC: 常盈完整副甲狀腺激素試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
I-PTH Standards:
One vial, 5 mL, labeled A, containing 0 pg/mL I-PTH and six vials, 1 mL each, labeled B-G, containing
approximate concentrations of 10, 30, 100, 250, 750 and 2000 pg/mL human PTH (1-84) in a protein-based
buffer with a non-mercury preservative.
* DSL-8000 (500 Tubes) contains three sets of standards
Anti-PTH-Coated Tubes: 
One hundred (100) plastic tubes with Anti-PTH (39-84) immobilized to the inside wall of each tube. 
* DSL-8000 (500 Tubes) contains five hundred (500) plastic tubes.

Anti-PTH [I-125] Reagent: 
Two vials in DSL-8000 (100 Tubes) , 5.5 mL each, containing <10 μCi (370 kBq) per vial of [I-125]-labeled
anti-PTH (1-34) in a protein-stabilized buffer and sodium azide as a preservative. 
* DSL-8000 (500 Tubes) contains ten (10) vials of reagent.
I-PTH Controls:
Two vials containing low and high concentrations of I-PTH in a protein-based buffer with a non-mercury
preservative.
* DSL-8000 (500 Tubes) contains three sets of controls.
Wash Concentrate:
One bottle, 100 mL, containing buffered saline with a nonionic detergent. 
* DSL-8000 (500 Tubes) contains five bottles of wash concentrate.
